      <body>
         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559"><!-- p1l1-r17 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-Hd1e108">Rubrica 17</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De voti religione</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-d1e114">
               ¶ Deuo<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>ti 
               religione. Rubrica. 17
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-Rd1e116">MOises in deutero. capitulo 33.</ref>
               <lb ed="#O"/> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-Qd1e123">Cum uoto domino deo tuo non 
               <lb ed="#O"/>tardabis reddere que requiret 
               <lb ed="#O"/>illud dominus deus tuus et si moratus 
               <lb ed="#O"/>fueris reputabit tibi in peccatum. 
               <lb ed="#O"/>Si olueris polliceri absque peccato 
               <lb ed="#O"/>eris.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-d1e144">
               <!--line bumps down-->
               <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-Rd1e143">Psa<!--line bumps up-->lmista. 49. psalmus.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-Qd1e148">Redde alti<!--line bumps down-->ssimo uota tua. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-d1e158">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-Rd1e157">75 psalmus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-Qd1e160">Uo<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>uete 
               et reddite domino deo vestro 
               <lb ed="#O"/>omnes qui in circuitum eius affertis 
               <lb ed="#O"/>munera.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-d1e166">
               <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-Rd1e169">Salam<!--line bumps up-->on in prouerb. capitulo 20.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-Qd1e170">Ru<!--line bumps down-->ina est homini deuouere sanctis 
               <lb ed="#O"/>et post vota tractare.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-d1e176">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-Rd1e179">Idem in 
               <lb ed="#O"/>ecclesiasto. capitulo 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-Qd1e178">Si quid vouisti deo ne 
               <lb ed="#O"/>moreris reddere: displicet enim ei infi<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>delis 
               et stulta promissio sed quodcunque 
               <lb ed="#O"/>uoueris redde multo melius est 
               <cb ed="#O" n="b"/>>
               <lb ed="#O"/>non uouere quam post uotum promissa 
               <lb ed="#O"/>non reddere. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-d1e192">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-Rd1e200">Isidorus <!--line bumps up--> soliloquiorum: libro 2. capitulo 36. <!--line bumps down--> </ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de4559-Qd1e196">In turpe votum muta de<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>cretum.
               ¶ Quod incaute nouisti 
               <lb ed="#O"/>non facias. Impia est promissio que 
               <lb ed="#O"/>scelere adimpletur.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
